{"tid":2357741,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"五年首次黨大會 稱經濟失策陷危機  金正恩憂失勢 認衰箍民心","createTime":"2021-01-07T15:48:07.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T18:05:57.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8b77018d683e11dba9951b468aa88ce7520e4f","tid":2357741,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210107/FZSUIWF3NFHUVKMYJ7STGY5NXQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210107%2FFZSUIWF3NFHUVKMYJ7STGY5NXQ%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z1KtFW5C59xXAvdsbQ2qrIE%3D&h=3da36670\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210107%2FFZSUIWF3NFHUVKMYJ7STGY5NXQ%2F&h=2e052a5b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210107/FZSUIWF3NFHUVKMYJ7STGY5NXQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n五年首次黨大會 稱經濟失策陷危機 <br />\n金正恩憂失勢 認衰箍民心<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/5K9NZLSI5MkdwT0-8w7678OP6l0=/1000x562/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/56P5HIH7WJHXPH2POHX53ECMVA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F5K9NZLSI5MkdwT0-8w7678OP6l0%3D%2F1000x562%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F56P5HIH7WJHXPH2POHX53ECMVA.jpg&h=1f776b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■金正恩出席第八次全國代表大會，承認上個經濟計劃未達標；妹妹金與正（箭嘴示）亦有參與。路透社<br />\n<br />\n相隔五年，北韓執政勞動黨再召開全國代表大會，黨委員長兼國家領袖金正恩前日開幕禮上承認，上一個經濟計劃幾乎完全未達標。分析指他去年起數次認錯，是想塑造愛民領袖形象，以防在武漢肺炎加劇的經濟危機中失勢。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：高層大換血 胞妹金與正獲重用<br />\n<br />\n官媒朝中社昨日報道，金正恩前一日在首都平壤為勞動黨第八次全國代表大會致開幕辭，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩形容國家正處於「多重危機」，目前面對的困難「前所未見」，相信是指聯合國所言、因國際制裁、武肺疫情和去年夏季水災而加劇的電力及糧食短缺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n武肺制裁交迫 GDP萎縮9.3%<br />\n<br />\n外界指，金正恩面前的或是他在位九年來最大挑戰。北韓為防疫封關近一年，有南韓經濟分析師指北韓與他最大、僅有的貿易夥伴中國，去年首11個月的貿易額比前年同期大跌約80%，估計北韓去年本地生產總值（GDP）萎縮9.3%。南韓情報機關去年11月亦指北韓入口貨如砂糖，價格增四倍，但同時工廠運作率卻因原材料短缺而跌至金正恩上台以來新低。<br />\n<br />\n金正恩上任初期，靠對外軍事。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n吹噓國際威望「奇蹟勝利」<br />\n<br />\n南韓國家戰略研究院學者申範徹（音譯）指，金正恩前日承認經濟失策似乎是「策略決定」，嘗試「鞏固自己的愛民領袖形象」。亦有分析指，經濟危機加劇、人民生活越趨困苦，或會削弱金正恩權威。<br />\n<br />\n但他前日仍不忘吹噓這五年的成就，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n大會有逾7,000人出席，相信會分數天進行，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fovMIrJl4WIFvI7pT3o3j_N9mVk=/640x600/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UQQDJUQC2NFBLFBOUR5TXAGS2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfovMIrJl4WIFvI7pT3o3j_N9mVk%3D%2F640x600%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUQQDJUQC2NFBLFBOUR5TXAGS2M.jpg&h=8f3adc6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■勞動黨再召開全國代表大會，平壤街頭有宣傳廣告。美聯社"},{"pid":"a51276639f177f43945daf5e1f99e6480895c6f4","tid":2357741,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:50:16.000Z","msg":"金仔都認錯 林奠呢"},{"pid":"0d2dadaf4152e2df4729d37273456f64eb70c214","tid":2357741,"uid":196329,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1q8Mvdn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1q8Mvdn.jpg&h=344537f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JwOTUE2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJwOTUE2.jpg&h=87f73a0d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"055572997a7a4b7158e3c740aa655fa448a81a73","tid":2357741,"uid":155818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"經濟失策??<br />\n有試過成功咩?"},{"pid":"e57d2d7e60db9dcb20504a5cf84a0b223da942ab","tid":2357741,"uid":292544,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T17:44:19.000Z","msg":"北韓有經濟架咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb9bf33c88320d608d5aba0f81c780d8490bd86b","tid":2357741,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T18:05:57.000Z","msg":"失勢？邊個夠膽嚟？<br />\n炮決！"}]}